              "height": 219,
              "content": "Okay don't need to be long-winded here. I think this is another interesting study where we're flexing the visual language that's applied to nodes. I think a lot of the thinking here is valid so I would consider how to carry this pattern forward although it's not much more divergent than the patterns we've already looked at. "
