              ],
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "ywhum",
                  "name": "sender",
                  "fill": "#807A6F",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "You",
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 10,
                  "fontWeight": "600",
                  "letterSpacing": 0.5
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "y4BwV",
                  "name": "message",
                  "fill": "#D4CDC0",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "What is the tradeoff between streaming tokens and batching full responses?",
                  "lineHeight": 1.45,
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 13,
                  "fontWeight": "normal",
                  "letterSpacing": 0.1
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "C8gtY",
              "x": 440,
              "y": 271,
              "name": "Node — Assistant Response 1",
              "width": 560,
              "fill": "#131210",
              "cornerRadius": 12,
              "stroke": {
                "align": "inside",
                "thickness": 1,
                "fill": "#252320"
              },
              "layout": "vertical",
              "gap": 6,
              "padding": [
                16,
                20
              ],
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "vBgQ1",
                  "name": "sender",
                  "fill": "#807A6F",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "Claude",
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 10,
                  "fontWeight": "600",
                  "letterSpacing": 0.5
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "vAWuE",
                  "name": "message",
                  "fill": "#D4CDC0",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "Streaming gives perceived speed. The user sees progress immediately. Batching gives you control over the final output before display. The tradeoff is responsiveness vs coherence. Most interfaces stream because waiting feels worse than watching.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.45,
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 13,
                  "fontWeight": "normal",
                  "letterSpacing": 0.1
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "QJIYa",
              "x": 440,
              "y": 413,
              "name": "Node — User Message 2",
              "width": 560,
              "fill": "#131210",
              "cornerRadius": 12,
              "stroke": {
                "align": "inside",
                "thickness": 1,
                "fill": "#252320"
              },
              "layout": "vertical",
              "gap": 6,
              "padding": [
                16,
                20
              ],
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "4axby",
                  "name": "sender",
                  "fill": "#807A6F",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "You",
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 10,
                  "fontWeight": "600",
                  "letterSpacing": 0.5
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "njiJq",
                  "name": "message",
                  "fill": "#D4CDC0",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "What if we batched but showed a progress skeleton instead of a spinner?",
                  "lineHeight": 1.45,
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 13,
                  "fontWeight": "normal",
                  "letterSpacing": 0.1
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "04htY",
              "x": 440,
              "y": 498,
              "name": "Node — Assistant Response 2",
              "width": 560,
              "fill": "#131210",
              "cornerRadius": 12,
              "stroke": {
                "align": "inside",
                "thickness": 1,
                "fill": "#252320"
              },
              "layout": "vertical",
              "gap": 6,
              "padding": [
                16,
                20
              ],
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "3PIhO",
                  "name": "sender",
                  "fill": "#807A6F",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "Claude",
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 10,
                  "fontWeight": "600",
                  "letterSpacing": 0.5
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "cPDtw",
                  "name": "message",
                  "fill": "#D4CDC0",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "That is a strong middle ground. A skeleton that reflects the expected structure gives the user a spatial preview without committing to streamed tokens. You would need response metadata prediction, but even a rough heuristic would feel better than a blank wait.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.45,
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 13,
                  "fontWeight": "normal",
                  "letterSpacing": 0.1
                }
              ]
            },
