                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": 400,
                      "content": "Same buttons expand to 6 positions on right-click\n4 cardinal positions at N/E/S/W on hover (200ms)\nRight-click escalates to radial with 2 extra actions\nSmooth 300ms spring animation to expand\nOnly one action highlighted at a time\nTooltip pill: E[3] bg, Inconsolata 8px, T.dim #404040",
                      "lineHeight": 1.8,
                      "fontFamily": "Inconsolata",
                      "fontSize": 10,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
