                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": 400,
                      "content": "Same icon buttons as cardinal, expanded to 6\nOrbit circle #252320, 1px stroke connects positions\n32px diameter buttons (larger than cardinal 20px)\nIcons: 14x14 lucide stroke icons\nHovered: fill E[5] #252320, border E[7] #3D3A35\nIcon hovered: T.secondary #C8C8C8\nCore dot: T.subtle #808080 (NOT amber/peach)",
                      "lineHeight": 1.8,
                      "fontFamily": "Inconsolata",
                      "fontSize": 10,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "MNdfR",
