                      "content": "Tier 0 (Common): Clean sphere, dim core T.dim #404040\nTier 1 (Uncommon): +1 orbital arc, core T.ghost #606060\nTier 2 (Rare): +arc +particles, core T.subtle #808080\nTier 3 (Epic): +breathing aura, core T.tertiary #A8A8A8\nTier 4 (Artifact): Brightest grey T.secondary #C8C8C8",
                      "lineHeight": 1.8,
                      "fontFamily": "Inconsolata",
                      "fontSize": 10,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "5xztU",
                      "name": "p1",
                      "fill": "#606060",
                      "content": "PROGRESSION RULES",
                      "fontFamily": "Inconsolata",
                      "fontSize": 11,
                      "fontWeight": "700",
                      "letterSpacing": 2
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "GO2I5",
                      "name": "p2",
                      "fill": "#404040",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": 380,
                      "content": "Warmth is NEVER applied. Grey luminance only.\nCore dot brightness earned through tier.\nOrbital arcs accumulate, never replace.\nSize grows with tier (48 → 64px).\nAccent color is RED #DD0000 — never peach.\nClassification: f(depth, branches, stars, saves)",
                      "lineHeight": 1.8,
                      "fontFamily": "Inconsolata",
                      "fontSize": 10,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
