              "y": 158,
              "width": 250,
              "height": 219,
              "content": "Okay this is more of an aesthetic study. I think I saved two subframes within this master subframe because I think what we're exploring is the use of the accent color red and how we can really make that feel alive and more dynamic as it's included within components across the system. I saved this purely to demonstrate how we could use the accent color red and in its use make the components feel more organic and alive."
