              "content": "Okay another nice study of the input field. We are overusing the peach cream color here in a few different areas but I think these treatments definitely indicate a great dynamicism of the input component. I think special mention: I really like the voice active state that you've created. I think this kind of feels very interesting and something that we'd want to continue to explore. While it's not perfect I think you're starting to get to an interesting output here. "
