              "id": "g0IuR",
              "layoutPosition": "absolute",
              "x": 827,
              "y": 68,
              "width": 250,
              "height": 219,
              "content": "Okay cool, I really like that this exploration is hyper minimal. I think there's a bit of borrowing from the system elements that I've sort of denoted as canonical but I do happen to like the ambition to keep at least this study and this collection of components relatively minimal. I think there's something nice about this and at least the kernel of the idea is something that we should carry forward in practice and memory."
            }
