              "id": "TE4E7",
              "x": 898.3119485914322,
              "y": 132.96893409245604,
              "width": 250,
              "height": 219,
              "content": "Okay included this one. I'm not sure why we generated the component for the session pill here and plotted it within a layout, which is sort of unnecessary. I think the thing to call out and pay attention to in this frame is the visual treatment and design style we applied to the session pill. I think this is something that feels very close to final so hats off to you on this. I think we will try to carry this pattern forward. "
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "note",
          "id": "bWLL3",
          "x": 1926,
          "y": 108,
          "width": 250,
          "height": 219,
          "content": "Okay this master frame contains a myriad of sub-frames that are collections of the design components that we built for the system. We've done a lot of great work. I'm gonna leave notes individually for each sub-page or sub-frame. Essentially what our objective here is to sort of pull together the final canonical versions of all the design components and document them appropriately so we can carry them forward in practice and memory. "
        },
        {
          "type": "note",
          "id": "ONziU",
          "x": 1767,
          "y": 10075,
          "width": 250,
          "height": 219,
          "content": "OK not much more to say about this component beyond that I like it and I like how minimal it is. It gives me a visual indication of system status and node count while not putting off too much visual noise and adding too much rich detail that might be undesirable as we're trying to keep the interface relatively minimal."
        }
      ]
    },
