              "width": 250,
              "height": 219,
              "content": "Okay so this is another attempt at the session drop down. I think some things are nice about this; others aren't. I think we got closer to a final execution of this component in an earlier iteration that I've already left a note on so I think we can kind of abandon this style. I mean it's not miles off from our brand and it does feel like we're veering close to what could be a final component. We just happen to have already solved this problem; we have the better standing example so I think we can consider this as something we can remove from the system altogether. Thanks. "
