            {
              "type": "note",
              "id": "5us8F",
              "layoutPosition": "absolute",
              "x": 464,
              "y": -87,
              "width": 250,
              "height": 219,
              "content": "Yeah okay so I think we've already nailed this component also but I would like to make a special mention that this treatment of the component uses the iconography or logos associated with each one of the AI models that would be part of the platform. I think that is a valid design decision that we want to carry forward. In an earlier true working session I introduced the SVG files for three AI models: Claude, GPT, and Gemini so you should already have those assets. We might want to colorize them to be on brand for those given AI providers. I think it's interesting to see the icons in situ and as part of a visual representation for that AI model and that selection. I think this pattern is valid for that reason. Although I think we have a better composition of the component in an earlier iteration, what we want to carry forward is the idea that we're using the logo or icon for each one of the AI models. "
            }
          ]
        },
