                  "name": "m3text",
                  "fill": "#A8A8A8",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "Right. What about a minimap in the corner that shows the full graph at a glance? Clicking a region zooms you there. Like a strategy game.",
